CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 6, 1946. pg. 17, reads: "Outdoors - With Summer now at its height, everyone is taking to the outdoors, and these young ladies are no exceptions. They are spending their vacations at Camp Carondawana, sponsored by the YMCA.  The girls are Martha Johnson, Sewickly; Eurelia Blake, Sewickley; Ruth Slosser, Bellevue; Lee Milner, Wilkes Barre, and Yvonne Taylor, Sewickley. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Martha Johnson, Eurelia Blake, Ruth Slosser, Lee Milner wearing bathing suit, and Yvonne Taylor, posed on porch of cabin at YMCA Camp Carondawana
